  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of three doses of XP19986 (arbaclofen placarbil) compared to placebo
      for the treatment of spasticity in subjects with multiple sclerosis (MS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
